data.description: Welcome to this incredibly unique A-frame style ranch home; where modern comfort meets extraordinary charm, in this meticulously updated 3-bedroom, 2-bathroom home. Step into a residence that effortlessly blends classic features with contemporary conveniences, making it the perfect haven for a modern lifestyle.  This home underwent significant upgrades in 2019 and 2020, including the roof, a heat pump hot water heater, a hybrid HVAC system that combines the heat pump and propane, and a water softener. These upgrades convey a sense of assurance for energy efficiency while meeting your daily needs. Embrace the benefits of solar energy with panels installed in 2020, contributing not only to sustainability but also to reduced utility costs.  Step inside to discover the inviting living area adorned with beautiful cathedral ceilings, creating an airy and spacious atmosphere. Automated skylight windows add a touch of sophistication, allowing natural light to flood the space. Marvel at the exposed beams, adding character and warmth to the interior.  This home is designed for easy living, featuring one-level convenience for your comfort. A charming breezeway connects the main residence to the patio area and a 2-car detached garage, providing a seamless transition between indoor and outdoor spaces. Additional storage is available in a well-maintained shed, catering to all your organizational needs.  Enjoy the privacy and security of a fenced-in rear yard, creating a tranquil oasis for relaxation and recreation. The unique combination of architectural features and modern updates sets this home apart, offering a distinctive and stylish living experience.  You’ll want to come see this home in person to truly appreciate how every detail has been thoughtfully curated to provide a harmonious and contemporary lifestyle. Welcome home to a residence that truly stands out.
